humanMachineDialogue.text: The report states that sentinel lymph nodes #1-#4, left axilla were all negative for tumor cells on touch prep and biopsy (0/1, 0/1, 0/2, 0/1 respectively). This indicates that there are no metastatic carcinomas in the sentinel lymph nodes and regional lymph nodes. Therefore, the N stage is N0, as per New Rule 10 and New Rule 11.
